  "html": "<body class=\"ParkSite\"><span aria-label=\"Top of page\" id=\"__topdoc__\" role=\"navigation\"></span>\n\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div id=\"beforeSkipLinks\" tabindex=\"-1\"></div>\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"GlobalHeader usaGlobalHeader\" role=\"banner\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-labelledby=\"exitModalLabel\" class=\"modal refreshableModal\" id=\"myModal\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h2 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"exitModalLabel\">Exiting nps.gov</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\"></div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Schedule\" id=\"cs_control_481716\"><div id=\"CS_Element_BannerContainer\" title=\"\"><div class=\"cs_GridRow\" id=\"gridRow_1_1_481716\"><div class=\"cs_GridColumn\" id=\"gridCol_1_1_1_1_481716\"><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_CustomCF\" id=\"cs_control_830326\"><div id=\"CS_CCF_1946213_830326\">\n\n</div></div><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_CustomCF\" id=\"cs_control_481855\"><div id=\"CS_CCF_1946213_481855\"> </div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div id=\"Park-header\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"pull-left\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n\n</div>\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div aria-label=\"Alerts Notification\" class=\"AlertsNotification\" data-site-code=\"grca\" id=\"AlertsNotification\" role=\"dialog\">\n<div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"AlertsNotification__Status visually-hidden\" role=\"status\">Loading alerts</div>\n<div class=\"collapse\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Panel\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Header\">\n<h2 class=\"Tag\" id=\"AlertsNotificationHeading\">Alerts In Effect</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Dismiss\" class=\"AlertsNotification__DismissButton\" type=\"button\">\nDismiss\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#close\"></use>\n</svg>\n</button>\n<span class=\"hr clearfix\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Body\" id=\"AlertsNotificationBody\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLinkContainer\">\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#add\"></use>\n</svg>\n<a class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLink\" href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/conditions.htm\" id=\"AlertsNotificationMoreLink\" tabindex=\"-1\">\nmore information on current conditions...\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"MainContent\" id=\"main\" role=\"main\">\n\n<div aria-labelledby=\"modal-contact-us-label\" class=\"modal fade\" id=\"modal-contact-us\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h4 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"modal-contact-us-label\">Contact Us</h4>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"adminTools\"></div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"ContentHeader text-content-size\">\n<h1 class=\"page-title\">Junior Ranger Family Programs</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Layout\" id=\"cs_control_2\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"CS_Layout_Table\" id=\"cs_idLayout2\" summary=\"\" width=\"100%\"><tr class=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x1x1\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_1946215\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<p>Check out the <a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/calendar.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=2623994,calendar.htm,11006|\">calendar </a>page for information of ranger programs, including family programming.</p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_6219475\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6219475\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<figure class=\"-left\">\n<picture>\n<source srcset=\"/grca/learn/kidsyouth/images/DSCN0554.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false&amp;quality=78&amp;format=webp\" type=\"image/webp\"/>\n<img alt=\"Park ranger leading a family group down an unpaved trail with trees in the background\" src=\"/grca/learn/kidsyouth/images/DSCN0554.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false\" title=\"Family Adventure Hike\"/>\n</picture>\n<figcaption>Park ranger leading a group of hikers into Grand Canyon </figcaption>\n</figure><!-- floating-image alignment  -->\n<p>During the summer, exploring with a ranger is a great way to learn about the park. <br/>\n</p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_6219524\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6219524\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<figure class=\"-left\">\n<picture>\n<source srcset=\"/grca/learn/kidsyouth/images/pine-smell.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false&amp;quality=78&amp;format=webp\" type=\"image/webp\"/>\n<img alt=\"A child smelling the bark of a large Ponderosa Pine tree\" src=\"/grca/learn/kidsyouth/images/pine-smell.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false\" title=\"A child smelling the bark of a large Ponderosa Pine tree\"/>\n</picture>\n<figcaption>A child smelling the vanilla-like fragrance of a Ponderosa Pine tree </figcaption>\n</figure><!-- floating-image alignment  -->\n<p>Exploring the world around you with all your senses is a great way to connect with nature in your backyard.</p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_6219513\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6219513\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<figure class=\"-left\">\n<picture>\n<source srcset=\"/grca/learn/kidsyouth/images/sunset-ranger.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false&amp;quality=78&amp;format=webp\" type=\"image/webp\"/>\n<img alt=\"Behind a silhouetted Ranger is a twilight sky after sunset\" src=\"/grca/learn/kidsyouth/images/sunset-ranger.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false\" title=\"Behind a silhouetted Ranger is a twilight sky after sunset\"/>\n</picture>\n<figcaption>Behind a silhouetted park ranger is a twilight sky after sunset. </figcaption>\n</figure><!-- floating-image alignment  -->\n<p>Experiencing the outdoors after the sun goes down introduces you to the beauty of the night skies and to the nocturnal creatures who like to be out when it's dark.</p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_6219531\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6219531\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<hr/>\n<h4>More information about <a href=\"/grca/learn/kidsyouth/junior-ranger.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1939782,/grca/learn/kidsyouth/junior-ranger.htm,14082|\" onmouseout=\"\" onmouseover=\"\">Becoming a Junior Ranger</a></h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Return to the <a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/ranger-program.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1902706,/grca/planyourvisit/ranger-program.htm,11006|\" onmouseout=\"\" onmouseover=\"\">Ranger Program Index Page</a></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/sr-programs.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=7551740,/grca/planyourvisit/sr-programs.htm,11006|\" onmouseout=\"\" onmouseover=\"\">South Rim Village</a> Ranger Programs</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/dv-programs.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=5499765,/grca/planyourvisit/dv-programs.htm,11006|\" onmouseout=\"\" onmouseover=\"\">Desert View</a> Ranger Program and Cultural Demonstrator Schedule. (On the South Rim, 24 miles east of Grand Canyon Village)</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/nr-programs.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=5499747,nr-programs.htm,11006|\">North Rim</a> Ranger Programs </li>\n</ul>\n</div></div>\n</td></tr>\n</table></div>\n</div><!-- col-sm-12 -->\n</div><!-- row -->\n</div><!-- ColumnMain col-sm-9 -->\n</div><!-- ColumnGrid row -->\n</div><!-- end container -->\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 text-content-size text-content-style\">\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\">Last updated: April 16, 2024</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n <!-- ParkFooter -->\n<!--googleon: index-->\n\n</div><!-- end of <div main> -->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!-- the rest of the scripts are leftovers from before the centennial down and should be pared down where possible -->\n\n<link href=\"/common/commonspot/templates/assets/libs/colorbox/colorbox.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n\n<div class=\"modal fade\" id=\"outdated-browser\" role=\"dialog\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n</div>\n</body>",
